The paper deals with video processing and understanding, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a generative model to learn compact latent codes also falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions compressive measurements and low-rank constraints, which are common in signal processing (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the regularization techniques used in the paper can also be considered as a form of optimization (cs.SI).
